### Description

I am trying to implement a subscription in company-list.component using the method getCompanies() from the company.service. However, I am encountering the following error:

Cannot read property 'subscribe' of undefined

From https://angulars.space/questions/issue-with-accessing-the-subscribe-property-in-nested-calls-within-angular-2-due-to-it-being-undefined

Here is the code snippet:

